          "title": "metaProof Launches Qripto",
          "type": "article",
          "format": "article",
          "content": {},
          "excerpt": "metaProof Launches Qripto At Q+AI Summit in NYC",
          "placement": {
            "tab": "",
            "imageX": 30,
            "imageY": 70,
            "section": "latest-news",
            "position": 1,
            "imageScale": 105,
            "imagePosition": "center"
          },
          "modalities": {
            "link": {
              "url": "https://quantumcomputingreport.com/metaproof-unveils-qripto-protocols-a-quantum-ready-internet-architecture/",
              "allow_embed": true
            },
            "read": {
              "text": "The metaProof Group unveiled its Quantum Ready Internet Protocols (Qripto), an open-source suite of protocols designed to power the “Internet of Trust.” The initiative is a multi-layered network intended to go beyond quantum resistance, focusing instead on unifying quantum capabilities, AI, and decentralized knowledge.\n\nThe Qripto initiative is built around three core protocols: iQube (knowledge), AigentiQ (intelligence), and COYN (value). These protocols are intended to allow data, AI, and digital currency to interoperate securely and contextually across quantum and blockchain networks. The suite aims to bridge the security of blockchain and the computational power of quantum computing with the intelligence of AI.\n\nThe company also announced QriptoCENT, a micro-stablecoin pegged to the U.S. penny. This micro-stablecoin is intended to facilitate secure, machine-to-machine transactions for AI agents, providing a mechanism for value exchange in a rapidly advancing quantum-agentic internet.\n\nDele Atanda, CEO of metaProof, noted that the protocols merge money with knowledge and intelligence, positioning the solution for the quantum age. The unveiling took place at the Q+AI Conference in New York City on October 20.",
              "duration": "1 min read"
            }
          },
          "media": {
            "thumbnail": "https://bsjhfvctmduxhohtllly.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/content-media/thumbnails/1764201286476-5nymeg.png",
            "hero": "https://bsjhfvctmduxhohtllly.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/content-media/thumbnails/1764201286476-5nymeg.png"
          },
