            "read": {
              "text": "# MoneyPenny\n\nMoneyPenny is your friendly guide to safer, smarter crypto—built for real people, not day traders. It helps you learn, practice, and (when you’re ready) run tiny, frequent Q¢ (QriptoCENT) trades that can add up over time—always with clear limits and plain-English explanations.\n\n## What it does\n\n* **Learns your rhythm (privately).** You can scan up to six months of bank statements. We don’t store the raw documents in the brain of the app. Instead, MoneyPenny turns them into simple numbers (like average surplus and monthly patterns) to tailor recommendations to *your* life.\n* **Watches the market for you.** It continuously checks live market conditions and compares them to your personal profile, so suggestions stay relevant and right-sized.\n* **Starts in Simulation Mode.** See quotes, “paper trades,” and potential earnings in real time—no risk. Flip to Live only when you feel ready.\n* **Keeps you in control.** You approve every action. Clear limits (daily loss caps, trade size, inventory range) are visible and easy to change.\n\n## How it works (in plain steps)\n\n1. Connect your wallet and (optionally) upload statements for a personalized setup.\n2. MoneyPenny sets sensible defaults for trade size, edge, and safety.\n3. It monitors prices and fees, then surfaces buy/sell opportunities you can approve.\n4. You track progress on a clean console with live updates and a running Q¢ tally.\n\n## Why it’s safe by design\n\n* **Privacy first:** Raw statements are sealed; the app uses **aggregates only** for recommendations.\n* **Consent at every step:** You choose what to share and when to go Live.\n* **Transparent by default:** Every suggestion comes with a brief “why.”\n\nMoneyPenny is here to make the complex feel comfortable—so you can build confidence, stay protected, and move at your own pace.\n",
              "duration": "2 min read"
            },
